---
// Hero.astro — Updated with real LinkedIn data
---

<header id="top" class="hero wrap">
  <div class="hero-status reveal">
    <span class="dot-live" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    Available for selected freelance &amp; consulting projects · 2026
  </div>

  <h1 class="hero-title">
    <span class="line"><span>Full-Stack</span></span>
    <span class="line"><span class="accent">Solution Architect</span></span>
    <span class="line"
      ><span class="outline">&amp; IT</span> <span>Manager</span></span
    >
  </h1>

  <p class="hero-sub reveal" data-d="2">
    Saya <strong>Isnaeni Hidayat</strong> — <strong>IT Manager</strong> &amp;
    <strong>Full-Stack Solution Architect</strong> yang membantu organisasi membangun
    sistem internal, workflow automation, ERP/Odoo customization, dashboard operasional,
    dan aplikasi bisnis berbasis AI. Lebih dari 10 tahun menangani pengembangan web
    end-to-end, dari arsitektur backend, integrasi API, database, hingga antarmuka
    yang rapi dan mudah digunakan.
  </p>

  <div class="hero-meta">
    <div class="item reveal" data-d="2">
      <div class="k"><span data-count="10" data-suffix="+">10+</span></div>
      <div class="l">Years building</div>
    </div>
    <div class="item reveal" data-d="3">
      <div class="k">
        <span data-count="4" data-suffix="+ yrs">4+ yrs</span>
      </div>
      <div class="l">Freelancing</div>
    </div>
    <div class="item reveal" data-d="4">
      <div class="k"><span data-count="5" data-suffix="+">5+</span></div>
      <div class="l">Companies served</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-actions reveal" data-d="3">
    <a
      href="#work"
      class="btn btn-primary"
      data-magnetic="0.3"
      id="hero-cta-work"
    >
      View Case Studies <span class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
    </a>
    <a
      href="#contact"
      class="btn btn-ghost"
      data-magnetic="0.3"
      id="hero-cta-contact"
    >
      Discuss a Project
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- tech marquee — real stack -->
  <div class="marquee reveal" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="marquee-track">
      <span>Laravel</span><span>Vue.js</span><span>Node.js</span><span
        >MySQL</span
      ><span>PostgreSQL</span><span>PHP</span><span>JavaScript</span><span
        >Odoo ERP</span
      ><span>REST API</span><span>Docker</span><span>Linux</span><span>Git</span
      >
      <span>Laravel</span><span>Vue.js</span><span>Node.js</span><span
        >MySQL</span
      ><span>PostgreSQL</span><span>PHP</span><span>JavaScript</span><span
        >Odoo ERP</span
      ><span>REST API</span><span>Docker</span><span>Linux</span><span>Git</span
      >
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-scroll" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="scroll-bar"></div>
    SCROLL
  </div>
</header>
